1
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:04,019
Continuing from before

2
00:02:05,060 --> 00:02:05,879
As the saying goes

3
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:09,520
A fearless youngster hits the county town

4
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:13,439
One phone call sparks a mix-up

5
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:16,939
The whole family jumps into action

6
00:02:17,699 --> 00:02:20,860
Going all-in on nails for a brighter future

7
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:22,960
As they say

8
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:25,240
A smile melts old grudges

9
00:02:25,659 --> 00:02:27,939
One laugh wipes the slate clean

10
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,919
But this time around

11
00:02:32,020 --> 00:02:32,580
Dandan's ordeal

12
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:33,599
