13
00:02:49,139 --> 00:02:51,159
Mr. Dongguo and the Wolf.

14
00:02:52,419 --> 00:02:54,879
You and your mother...

15
00:02:56,699 --> 00:02:57,860
You're gonna be the death of me!

16
00:02:58,060 --> 00:02:58,900
You little ingrate!

17
00:03:00,659 --> 00:03:01,620
It's not my fault.

18
00:03:01,939 --> 00:03:02,560
Talking back now?

19
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,699
It's for your own good, so I'm wrong?

20
00:03:04,919 --> 00:03:07,120
I mean, Mr. Dongguo was also wrong.

21
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:08,699
What did Mr. Dongguo do wrong?

22
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,939
He saw the wolf about to be killed by hunters,

23
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:11,780
