24
00:03:12,139 --> 00:03:12,900
Wasn't that for its own good?

25
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,860
He could tell at a glance it was a wolf.

26
00:03:15,699 --> 00:03:16,060
What if...

27
00:03:17,319 --> 00:03:18,599
What if it was a Husky?

28
00:03:19,539 --> 00:03:20,759
Full of twisted logic!

29
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,740
You think talking your way out

30
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:24,500
