31
00:03:27,259 --> 00:03:27,520
Go!

32
00:03:28,979 --> 00:03:30,319
Bring me that feather duster.

33
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:39,439
Yang Fanmei!

34
00:03:39,699 --> 00:03:41,120
You're not gonna beat me again, are you?

35
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:42,520
That's right!

36
00:03:44,620 --> 00:03:45,740
You little rascal!

37
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:46,520
You even know

38
00:03:47,099 --> 00:03:48,340
