39
00:03:48,699 --> 00:03:49,159
You little...

40
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,340
You dared to run away from home?

41
00:03:50,340 --> 00:03:51,800
I'll teach you a lesson!

42
00:03:54,060 --> 00:03:54,620
Stop right there!

43
00:03:55,979 --> 00:03:57,639
How dare you run away from home!

44
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:01,439
Qian Zhenqing,

45
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,520
what Mr. Dongguo and the Wolf?

46
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:05,680
If you're gonna hit the kid, just do it.

47
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,900
Stingy old man!

48
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:16,060
Won't even spring for a full set of bulbs.

49
00:04:58,740 --> 00:04:59,019
Mom

50
00:04:59,019 --> 00:04:59,959
You finally called me.

51
00:05:00,279 --> 00:05:01,420
I couldn't call during the day.

52
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:02,959
Your dad's always watching me.

53
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,339
