54
00:05:04,980 --> 00:05:05,879
So is he asleep yet?

55
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,699
Right now?

56
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,360
He's fast asleep.

57
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:10,180
Snoring away.

58
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,120
Then hurry up and send it to me!

59
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,779
I can't transfer it by bank card.

60
00:05:15,220 --> 00:05:16,779
If I use the bank card,

61
00:05:17,019 --> 00:05:18,360
