64
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,220
Mom,

65
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,120
I really want to go study painting.

66
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,779
I don't want to follow my brother

67
00:05:25,779 --> 00:05:26,620
