74
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,060
I'll bring it to you tomorrow.

75
00:05:45,339 --> 00:05:46,519
Give me your address.

76
00:05:47,180 --> 00:05:48,740
The address is Donghua Avenue.

77
00:05:48,980 --> 00:05:50,360
