78
00:05:50,819 --> 00:05:51,980
Anyway, there's an art class there.

79
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,639
It's called Sunflower Art Class.

80
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:55,800
Did you get that?

81
00:05:56,259 --> 00:05:56,819
Got it.

82
00:05:59,360 --> 00:05:59,959
Alright, son.

83
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,680
I'll bring it over tomorrow.

84
00:06:02,279 --> 00:06:03,259
That's it. Hanging up.

85
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:07,980
This one looks nice.

86
00:07:08,100 --> 00:07:08,819
Pretty cool, right?

87
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,519
Can you do this one?

88
