It's actually not that hard.

89
00:07:12,439 --> 00:07:12,980
Look here.

90
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,319
First, paint on the color.

91
00:07:14,319 --> 00:07:15,860
Then blend with a sponge, add rhinestones.

92
00:07:15,939 --> 00:07:17,899
Finally, seal it with crystal topcoat.

93
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,399
And it's done.

94
00:07:18,980 --> 00:07:19,579
You're amazing.

95
00:07:19,579 --> 00:07:20,819
