134
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,199
Right?

135
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:33,220
You hear me?

136
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:35,100
When she's gone, you'll be sorry.

137
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:37,200
All right, all right.

138
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,320
That's enough.

139
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:05,720
