178
00:10:16,539 --> 00:10:17,539
Look, Huanhuan.

179
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,700
I'm already at this age.

180
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,080
I've been on my own,

181
00:10:21,100 --> 00:10:22,039
