264
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,019
No, no, no

265
00:13:43,139 --> 00:13:43,600
Count it, count it

266
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,399
No need

267
00:13:44,559 --> 00:13:45,179
Just count it, count it

268
00:13:45,220 --> 00:13:45,659
It's enough

269
00:13:45,659 --> 00:13:46,720
If you don't count, I will

