622
00:27:53,579 --> 00:27:55,619
Your... your mom what?

623
00:27:56,220 --> 00:27:57,940
The kind where hitting doesn't hurt.

624
00:27:58,759 --> 00:28:00,400
The kind where hitting doesn't hurt.

625
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:00,859
Right?

626
00:28:01,039 --> 00:28:02,480
Come here, you.

627
00:28:02,559 --> 00:28:04,220
Looks like you're asking for a beating.

628
00:28:05,279 --> 00:28:06,660
Great acting, Dandan.

629
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:07,740
Does it hurt?

630
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:08,559
Dad.

631
00:28:09,460 --> 00:28:10,720
I'll give you ten percent shares.

632
00:28:10,839 --> 00:28:11,500
Just help us take care of

633
