Don't try to fool me!

677
00:31:00,460 --> 00:31:02,079
Even when I'm grown, I won't get a cent.

678
00:31:02,559 --> 00:31:03,279
When I grow up,

679
00:31:03,279 --> 00:31:04,519
I'm going far away from you,

680
00:31:05,079 --> 00:31:06,059
