702
00:32:14,259 --> 00:32:14,799
Not just me.

703
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:16,660
Bro has shares too.

704
00:32:17,880 --> 00:32:19,119
Everyone put in

705
00:32:19,119 --> 00:32:20,000
