739
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:26,359
Great taste!

740
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:26,980
Great taste!

741
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:28,619
She's her, I'm me.

742
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,779
Our money has to be kept separate.

743
