Others rely on Children as old-age security.

744
00:33:33,119 --> 00:33:33,779
But you?

745
00:33:33,940 --> 00:33:34,839
You guard against your own mom at every turn.

746
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:36,140
That's because you never keep your word.

747
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:36,740
You borrow my money and never pay it back.

748
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,180
Xiaofang.

749
