752
00:33:40,420 --> 00:33:41,140
I paid those back too.

753
00:33:41,339 --> 00:33:42,160
That's weird.

754
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:43,839
So early in the morning,

755
00:33:43,839 --> 00:33:45,039
