777
00:34:41,579 --> 00:34:42,699
Won't even call me "Mom"

778
00:34:44,059 --> 00:34:45,420
She's still too young to understand

779
00:34:46,360 --> 00:34:47,099
Girls...

780
00:34:47,719 --> 00:34:48,380
Once she grows up a bit

781
00:34:48,699 --> 00:34:50,280
