811
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,039
How about this

812
00:36:00,340 --> 00:36:01,820
You give me 40,000 first

813
00:36:02,659 --> 00:36:03,820
Once the investment matures

814
00:36:04,039 --> 00:36:04,860
I'll pay back the 40,000

815
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,119
And the dividends from it

816
00:36:06,219 --> 00:36:06,900
