830
00:36:41,619 --> 00:36:43,139
The nail salon money for my retirement.

831
00:36:43,860 --> 00:36:45,119
No pressure, huh?

832
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,639
What if we lose money?

833
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:47,559
