843
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:00,820
A matter of life and death.

844
00:37:00,840 --> 00:37:02,119
You gotta have that "come what may" spirit.

845
00:37:02,179 --> 00:37:02,539
Right.

846
00:37:02,639 --> 00:37:03,820
Come what may, huh?

847
00:37:04,119 --> 00:37:05,699
