850
00:37:09,699 --> 00:37:11,199
We won't lose money.

851
00:37:11,579 --> 00:37:12,619
You're all confident, right?

852
00:37:12,619 --> 00:37:13,340
Yes!

853
00:37:13,340 --> 00:37:14,380
Yes! Yes!

854
00:37:14,699 --> 00:37:15,460
Yes!

855
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:16,480
Yes!

856
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:17,619
That's more like it.

857
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,559
You want in too?

858
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,019
No objections.

859
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,639
What's there to object to?

860
00:37:25,139 --> 00:37:26,599
It's just spending money, right?

861
00:37:28,119 --> 00:37:29,360
I mean, all this time,

862
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:31,619
our family's been pinned at the top

863
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:34,320
of the village gossip headlines.

864
00:37:35,980 --> 00:37:38,980
This is the best time for a Desperate comeback.

865
00:37:39,719 --> 00:37:40,639
This Mid-Autumn Festival,

866
00:37:40,739 --> 00:37:41,659
