868
00:37:43,719 --> 00:37:44,800
I want everyone in the village

869
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:46,539
to look at us with envy.

870
00:37:50,099 --> 00:37:51,800
Fanmei's such a big mouth.

871
00:37:52,119 --> 00:37:52,960
Almost blew our cover.

872
00:37:59,760 --> 00:38:01,280
Take this and buy some gifts.

873
