Sis, you sure love a good ceremony.

874
00:38:04,679 --> 00:38:06,159
Who are these gifts for?

875
00:38:07,579 --> 00:38:09,480
After all this mess between Xiaofang and the Qi family,

876
00:38:09,739 --> 00:38:10,420
and just a while back,

877
00:38:10,420 --> 00:38:11,380
we had that whole fiasco

878
00:38:11,380 --> 00:38:12,639
with her running away from home.

879
00:38:13,239 --> 00:38:14,159
The folks who came to help,

880
00:38:14,539 --> 00:38:16,039
