886
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:26,760
Her dad's definitely tight on cash.

887
00:38:27,139 --> 00:38:28,639
Your Old Qian just went bankrupt again.

888
00:38:29,619 --> 00:38:30,639
Can't count on him either.

889
00:38:32,820 --> 00:38:34,099
All the holiday money this year,

890
00:38:34,420 --> 00:38:35,219
I'm covering it all.

891
00:38:36,079 --> 00:38:37,420
I'm being so generous to you two.

892
00:38:37,460 --> 00:38:38,219
Shouldn't you

893
00:38:38,300 --> 00:38:39,440
save me some money too?

894
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:40,460
Fine.

895
00:38:41,179 --> 00:38:42,260
Thanks a lot.

896
00:38:42,719 --> 00:38:43,980
I'll buy on a budget.

897
00:38:46,619 --> 00:38:48,599
Make sure it's cheap but nice,

898
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:49,800
something presentable.

899
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:52,019
You know, the kind with flashy packaging,

900
00:38:52,260 --> 00:38:53,059
what's inside

901
