902
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:56,559
Me, I've got something too.

903
00:38:56,639 --> 00:38:59,000
Go buy me some fireworks and firecrackers.

904
00:38:59,320 --> 00:39:00,320
The kind where one bang

905
