912
00:39:13,659 --> 00:39:15,099
Set off some firecrackers, Blast away the bad luck.

913
00:39:15,840 --> 00:39:17,699
Sis, those big fireworks you're talking about,

914
00:39:17,699 --> 00:39:19,320
