918
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:25,539
Go find the fireworks seller,

919
00:39:25,579 --> 00:39:26,139
and tell him,

920
00:39:26,139 --> 00:39:26,960
the ones stashed at the bottom,

921
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:28,019
the ones that won't sell,

922
00:39:28,260 --> 00:39:28,559
