925
00:39:32,500 --> 00:39:33,960
So, dud firecrackers, right?

926
00:39:34,300 --> 00:39:35,739
Fine, I'll do my best, my best.

927
00:39:36,559 --> 00:39:37,920
Sis, why are you slipping in loose change?

928
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:40,619
Genius.

929
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,360
What are you up to now?

930
00:39:42,579 --> 00:39:43,599
Letting the whole village

931
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:46,239
