932
00:39:46,639 --> 00:39:48,900
And let Bit soak up some blessings too.

933
00:39:50,539 --> 00:39:51,619
Look at Sis's grand vision.

934
00:39:51,659 --> 00:39:52,719
Big sis is big sis.

935
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:53,639
On top of the fridge,

936
00:39:54,079 --> 00:39:56,980
