937
00:39:57,159 --> 00:39:57,760
You two go check it out.

938
00:39:58,579 --> 00:39:59,360
Okay, let's have a look.

939
00:39:59,860 --> 00:40:01,880
See what tasty stuff there is.

940
00:40:02,460 --> 00:40:04,679
The reunion dinner menu's all set.

941
00:40:11,659 --> 00:40:12,340
Big sis

942
00:40:12,639 --> 00:40:13,880
For the holidays these days, other families

943
00:40:13,900 --> 00:40:16,099
