944
00:40:16,219 --> 00:40:16,960
It symbolizes that

945
00:40:16,980 --> 00:40:17,840
the whole family can Walk sideways like a boss.

946
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,300
Let's get a king crab too.

947
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:20,719
Yeah!

948
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:21,800
Let's get some

949
00:40:21,820 --> 00:40:23,139
fresh stuff to eat too.

950
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:25,000
Stop making the same old three dishes.

951
00:40:25,260 --> 00:40:26,059
We're sick of them.

952
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:29,099
I'm telling you,

953
00:40:29,139 --> 00:40:29,960
just look at him,

954
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:30,960
All hunched over.

955
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:32,400
Slap a shell on your back

956
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,300
and shove you right in the water,

957
00:40:33,340 --> 00:40:34,079
you could just swim away.

958
00:40:34,519 --> 00:40:35,019
And you,

959
00:40:35,599 --> 00:40:36,280
here in the village,

960
00:40:36,500 --> 00:40:37,639
all dressed up in fancy colors,

961
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:38,960
