962
00:40:39,159 --> 00:40:40,019
A Peacock!

963
00:40:40,539 --> 00:40:41,579
The two of you together

964
00:40:41,739 --> 00:40:42,760
make a famous dish,

965
00:40:43,119 --> 00:40:44,260
Farewell My Concubine.

966
00:40:45,119 --> 00:40:45,980
You're really proving the saying,

967
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:47,079
"Beggars can't be choosers."

968
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:47,780
Unbelievable.

969
00:40:49,139 --> 00:40:49,820
This money of mine

970
00:40:49,900 --> 00:40:51,579
has to be saved for Xiaofang and Jingjing,

971
00:40:51,619 --> 00:40:53,199
to buy each of them a new outfit.

972
00:40:53,679 --> 00:40:55,000
