973
00:40:56,719 --> 00:40:57,679
He won't be left out.

974
00:41:06,440 --> 00:41:08,119
An old tree blossoms anew

975
00:41:09,340 --> 00:41:09,960
Looks great

976
00:41:10,739 --> 00:41:11,260
Grandma

977
00:41:11,619 --> 00:41:12,719
This is just the basic one

978
00:41:12,719 --> 00:41:14,619
I only put some color on for you

979
00:41:14,900 --> 00:41:16,980
Once our nail salon opens up

980
00:41:17,059 --> 00:41:17,900
And we've got all the supplies

981
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:20,800
I'll give you a handmade reinforcement

982
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,880
Plus the complete set of

983
00:41:21,960 --> 00:41:22,800
