984
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:23,599
That'll be amazing

985
00:41:23,679 --> 00:41:25,059
Don't forget the toenails either

986
00:41:25,079 --> 00:41:26,639
Grandma's gonna be the trendiest one

987
00:41:27,579 --> 00:41:28,420
Wonderful

988
00:41:30,739 --> 00:41:31,800
Do you girls have money?

989
00:41:32,920 --> 00:41:33,840
Grandma has money

990
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:35,579
Yes

991
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,599
Don't worry, Grandma

992
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:38,760
Just keep your money safe

993
00:41:40,280 --> 00:41:41,280
Then when it opens

994
00:41:41,579 --> 00:41:42,920
I'll bring all my old sisters

995
00:41:43,079 --> 00:41:44,460
