996
00:41:44,659 --> 00:41:46,260
But when they sign up

997
00:41:46,480 --> 00:41:47,480
give them a discount, okay?

998
00:41:47,559 --> 00:41:48,699
Absolutely

999
00:41:50,480 --> 00:41:52,280
What are you all talking about? So happy

1000
00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:53,300
Look

1001
00:41:53,780 --> 00:41:54,920
Jingjing did this for me

1002
00:41:55,739 --> 00:41:56,480
Pretty, right?

1003
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:57,500
Really pretty

1004
00:41:58,159 --> 00:41:59,320
I'm heading to town

1005
00:41:59,719 --> 00:42:01,059
Want me to pick anything up?

1006
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:02,599
I want durian

1007
00:42:03,139 --> 00:42:04,019
Okay, durian it is

1008
00:42:05,599 --> 00:42:05,980
Mom

1009
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:07,980
I've washed this blanket for you

1010
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:08,539
It's all dry now

1011
00:42:09,239 --> 00:42:09,800
Drape it over there

1012
00:42:11,719 --> 00:42:12,079
Alright

1013
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:13,260
Well

1014
00:42:14,380 --> 00:42:14,760
Xiaofang

1015
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:15,719
You be careful

1016
00:42:15,800 --> 00:42:16,559
Don't move around too much

1017
00:42:16,699 --> 00:42:18,059
