1018
00:42:18,199 --> 00:42:19,480
Don't strain yourself, okay?

1019
00:42:19,719 --> 00:42:21,320
Go on, I'll watch her

1020
00:42:23,539 --> 00:42:24,199
Well then

1021
00:42:26,079 --> 00:42:26,500
Okay

1022
00:42:27,820 --> 00:42:28,440
Bye, Auntie

1023
