1038
00:43:03,699 --> 00:43:05,880
You just love winding up my daughter, huh?

1039
00:43:08,260 --> 00:43:08,659
Look

1040
00:43:09,119 --> 00:43:09,619
Does it look good?

1041
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:11,940
It looks good

1042
00:43:23,780 --> 00:43:25,880
A lot has happened recently

1043
00:43:26,360 --> 00:43:27,619
And I've done a lot of things wrong

1044
00:43:29,019 --> 00:43:30,099
No matter how you see me

1045
00:43:31,239 --> 00:43:31,800
I accept it

1046
00:43:33,239 --> 00:43:34,360
Yang Xiaofang

1047
00:43:35,659 --> 00:43:37,239
I love you

1048
00:43:39,659 --> 00:43:41,139
You're all in on this together to fool me

1049
00:43:41,639 --> 00:43:43,420
I guess I'm not family, huh?

1050
00:43:44,940 --> 00:43:46,719
Take that! Take that!

1051
00:43:48,519 --> 00:43:49,000
Stop

1052
00:43:50,599 --> 00:43:51,659
How did I wet myself?

